1/ Create a file 
gettext_example.py

2/ build the pot file
POT = PO template file ?

3/ cp POT file in ./locale/en_US/LC_MESSAGES/ as PO file
Note that we don't have control over the directory structure

4/ edit manually PO file and add translation

5/ edit manually the PO file CHARSET
In PO file chane
"Content-type: text/plain; charset=CHARSET\n"
with 
"Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"

5/ build mo file 
cd ./locale/en_US/LC_MESSAGES/
msgfmt -o gettext_example.mo gettext_example.po                         # <-- MO file is not editable manually

6/ execute initial program 
python gettext_example.py
!!! The locale directory should be in the directory when the python script is exectuted!
